Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Adjoining UTS and opposite Central Park

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
13 Broadway is located near the intersection of Broadway and Harris Street with thousands of commuters passing daily. The tenancy adjoins UTS and is directly opposite Central Park. 

We are seeking a long-term lease and there is the opportunity for long trading hours to capitalise on busy pedestrian ant-track.

- 69.9sqm tenancy (approx.)
- Significant frontage and branding opportunities
- On-grade entry off Broadway
- Rear amenity and storage
- High floor-to-ceiling heights
- Substantial foot traffic
- Suitable for light food & beverage (no grease or exhaust available)
- 7-day retail precinct
- Immediate availability!

725 Harris Street is located near the intersection of Broadway and Harris Street with thousands of commuters passing daily. The tenancy includes 15 metres of glass frontage overlooking Harris Street, UTS Design & Architecture Faculty and ABC Ultimo offices. 

We are seeking long-term lease with an opportunity for long trading hours to capitalise on surrounding university and commercial market.

- 122sqm tenancy (approx)
- Significant frontage and branding opportunities
- Two entry doors off Harris Street
- High floor-to-ceiling heights
- Substantial foot traffic
- No grease or exhaust available
- Suitable for retail users
- Immediate availability!

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: LARGE RETAIL FOR LEASE – ADJOINING UTS

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to present 619-621 Harris Street, Ultimo, a prominent three-storey, freehold building in one of Sydney’s thriving City Fringe suburbs.
619-621 Harris Street, Ultimo benefits from the following key attributed:

- Desirable Sydney city fringe location on the border of the Sydney CBD
- Ideal owner occupier investment
- Centred in Sydney’s creative and educational precinct
- Located 600m* from Central Station and on the border of the Sydney CBD
- Dual access with 7 car spaces
- Offered with a short term lease
- Large net lettable area of 665sqm*
